Class BranchPropertyAccessorImpl

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAccessor, IPropertyAccessor, Cloneable

    public final class BranchPropertyAccessorImpl
extends AbstractPropertyAccessorImpl
    The final class BranchPropertyAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing properties that are instances of PropertyClass annotated classes.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
